Subject: Intro of Morning Star


> (OOC: Hi, I'm new to this group, but I'm involved in another RPG so I
> hope it won't be too different.)
>
> A streak of light moves across the prehistoric sky as the small ship
> enters the atmosphere.  A computer voice drowns out the rumbling of the
> ship.  "DAMAGE TO TRANSWARP ENGINES.  HULL BREACH IN SECTOR 3.
> MANEUVERING CAPABILITIES AT 37 PERCENT."  The pilot says only one
> word..."Slag."  As the ship continues to plummet, the Pilot prepares for
> impact.
>
> The crater formed from the crash is roughly 250 ft in diameter and 100 ft
> deep.  out of the burning wreckage flies a glowing shape.  A trail of
> fire stretches behind him creating the image of a comet.  When he arrives
> at the Predicon base, the flames die out and a giant red, gold, and
> purple bird is standing in their place.  "Morning Star...Terrorize."
> Parts shift and rotate as the robot transforms into robot mode.
> "Predicon commander, do you read me?  This is Morning Star.  I am here to
> help your cause."
